column2: SELECT m.ra AS ra1, m.dec AS dec1, m.name as redshift, n.objID, n.distance, p.ra AS ra2, p.dec AS dec2, p.modelMag_u, p.modelMagErr_u, p.modelMag_g, p.modelMagErr_g, p.modelMag_r, p.modelMagErr_r, p.modelMag_i, p.modelMagErr_i, p.modelMag_z, p.modelMagErr_z, psfMag_r, psfMagErr_r, psfMag_i, psfMagErr_i, psfMag_z, psfMagErr_z, p.cModelMag_r, p.cModelMagErr_r p.cModelMag_i, p.cModelMagErr_i, p.fiberMag_i , p.fiberMagErr_i, p.deVRad_i , p.deVRadErr_i into BOSS_CMASS_HSC_Gal_Photobj_new FROM MyDB.BOSS_CMASS_HSC_RA_DEC AS m CROSS APPLY dbo.fGetNearestObjEq (m.ra, m.dec, #) AS n JOIN PhotoObj AS p ON n.objID = p.objID
